title: Person of Interest - 5x12 '.exe' - Sneak Peek #2
author: POISuit
comment: TESLA? FOR REAL?! THIS IS THE BEST SHOW EVER

The way the music goes sinister when Reese says that Finch might kill Greer is so terrifying. Elias was absolutely right, he is the most dangerous one when his rage activates. Never have I been so scared of a good fictional character that turned rogue!
There's no driver in the car?
